{"root":{"data":{"text":"售后故障流程"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"售后部门"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"开始：售后故障流程"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"获取故障现象"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"判断是否为已知问题?"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"是"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"与用户沟通处理"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"接收解决方案 (用户/其他)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"问题解决"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"跳转至通用问题判断"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"否"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"安抚用户"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"接收安抚与进度同步 (用户/其他)"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"同步销售/上级"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"接收信息 (销售/上级)"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"判定故障等级"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"执行响应动作"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"提交相应工单"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"接收工单及用户详情 (产线部门)"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"完成故障排查 (产线部门)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"text":"同步排查情况 (产线部门)"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"接收产线同步情况"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"同步最终情况给各方 (用户、销售、上级)"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"接收最终处理结果 (用户/其他)"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"判断是否为通用问题?"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"是"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"内部知识库记录"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"否"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"内部记录故障详情"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"text":"结束"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}